name: Isaac Newton
comment: My wife thought we should get divorced. After speaking with Dr. Eshan Benjamin we saw a new future for our marriage. Thank you Coach for your help!

name: selina Gomez
comment: I was afraid to switch my job to something different. Now I feel that this was the best decision I ever made. Do not be afraid to act!

name: Taylor Swift
comment: It was a relief to know that you are not the only one with a problem of a broken heart. I appreciate the support and joy of your seminars!

name: Elon Musk
comment: Most of the time we do not realize how great life is. Dr. Eshan Benjamin helps people start feeling alive and believe in themselves!

name: Alexandra Daddario
comment: Being a single mom makes your life miserable. If it wasn't for Judie, I would have lost it. Now I know it is never too late to ask for help.
